snippet.title: CABAL Online Episode XVI: Legends Unleashed
snippet.description:
On October 6th, witness the return of Baldus in this brand new update for CABAL Online! With brand new class skills, accessories and a challenging battle arena, players must overcome the ultimate test of skill to emerge as the hero of Nevareth. 

Will it be you?
